What is the surface area of a cube with a side length of 12 inches?

Surface area...................
S = ph + 2B
S = (4 * 12)(12) + 2(12 * 12)
S = 576 + 288
S = 864

Check..........................
12^2 = S/6
12^2 = 864/6
144 = 144

